Chat App by Sanhil❤️


A chat app with group chat functionality is a communication platform that allows users to engage in real-time conversations with multiple participants. It goes beyond one-on-one conversations and facilitates group discussions, collaboration, and coordination. This overview will explore the key features and benefits of such an app.


Key Features:

1. Group Creation: Users can create groups and invite others to join. Groups can be based on various criteria such as interests, projects, organizations, or social circles.

2. Member Management: Group admins have the ability to manage group membership, including adding or removing members.

3. Privacy and Security: Robust privacy and security measures are implemented to protect user data and conversations. These measures may include end-to-end encryption, and secure server infrastructure.